{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1235,"text":"Everything I do, and everything I do professionally --"},{"time":4714,"text":"my life -- has been shaped"},{"time":8699,"text":"by seven years of work as a young man in Africa."},{"time":14523,"text":"From 1971 to 1977 --"},{"time":18044,"text":"I look young, but I'm not — (Laughter) --"},{"time":21924,"text":"I worked in Zambia, Kenya, Ivory Coast, Algeria, Somalia,"},{"time":26857,"text":"in projects of technical cooperation with African countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31074,"text":"I worked for an Italian NGO,"},{"time":34192,"text":"and every single project that we set up in Africa"},{"time":40342,"text":"failed."},{"time":43786,"text":"And I was distraught."},{"time":47930,"text":"I thought, age 21, that we Italians were good people"},{"time":52178,"text":"and we were doing good work in Africa."},{"time":55560,"text":"Instead, everything we touched we killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62573,"text":"Our first project, the one that has inspired my first book,"},{"time":67676,"text":"\"Ripples from the Zambezi,\""},{"time":70564,"text":"was a project where we Italians"},{"time":73129,"text":"decided to teach Zambian people how to grow food."},{"time":79050,"text":"So we arrived there with Italian seeds in southern Zambia"},{"time":83399,"text":"in this absolutely magnificent valley"},{"time":86879,"text":"going down to the Zambezi River,"},{"time":90132,"text":"and we taught the local people how to grow Italian tomatoes"},{"time":93760,"text":"and zucchini and ..."},{"time":96551,"text":"And of course the local people had absolutely no interest"},{"time":98746,"text":"in doing that, so we paid them to come and work,"},{"time":101661,"text":"and sometimes they would show up. (Laughter)"},{"time":105796,"text":"And we were amazed that the local people,"},{"time":108523,"text":"in such a fertile valley, would not have any agriculture."},{"time":111610,"text":"But instead of asking them how come they were not"},{"time":114818,"text":"growing anything, we simply said, \"Thank God we're here.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":118840,"text":"\"Just in the nick of time to save the Zambian people from starvation.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":123508,"text":"And of course, everything in Africa grew beautifully."},{"time":126968,"text":"We had these magnificent tomatoes. In Italy, a tomato"},{"time":129626,"text":"would grow to this size. In Zambia, to this size."},{"time":133235,"text":"And we could not believe, and we were telling the Zambians,"},{"time":136056,"text":"\"Look how easy agriculture is.\""},{"time":138528,"text":"When the tomatoes were nice and ripe and red,"},{"time":141539,"text":"overnight, some 200 hippos came out from the river"},{"time":144967,"text":"and they ate everything. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":148970,"text":"And we said to the Zambians, \"My God, the hippos!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":153554,"text":"And the Zambians said, \"Yes, that's why we have no agriculture here.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":159235,"text":"\"Why didn't you tell us?\"\"You never asked.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":165487,"text":"I thought it was only us Italians blundering around Africa,"},{"time":170575,"text":"but then I saw what the Americans were doing,"},{"time":173319,"text":"what the English were doing, what the French were doing,"},{"time":176055,"text":"and after seeing what they were doing,"},{"time":178648,"text":"I became quite proud of our project in Zambia."},{"time":182007,"text":"Because, you see, at least we fed the hippos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186996,"text":"You should see the rubbish — (Applause) --"},{"time":191243,"text":"You should see the rubbish that we have bestowed"},{"time":193737,"text":"on unsuspecting African people."},{"time":195537,"text":"You want to read the book,"},{"time":197113,"text":"read \"Dead Aid,\" by Dambisa Moyo,"},{"time":202044,"text":"Zambian woman economist."},{"time":205051,"text":"The book was published in 2009."},{"time":207421,"text":"We Western donor countries have given the African continent"},{"time":211995,"text":"two trillion American dollars in the last 50 years."},{"time":216988,"text":"I'm not going to tell you the damage that that money has done."},{"time":220813,"text":"Just go and read her book."},{"time":223001,"text":"Read it from an African woman, the damage that we have done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231364,"text":"We Western people are imperialist, colonialist missionaries,"},{"time":237331,"text":"and there are only two ways we deal with people:"},{"time":240645,"text":"We either patronize them, or we are paternalistic."},{"time":245034,"text":"The two words come from the Latin root \"pater,\""},{"time":248138,"text":"which means \"father.\""},{"time":250368,"text":"But they mean two different things."},{"time":254221,"text":"Paternalistic, I treat anybody from a different culture"},{"time":257582,"text":"as if they were my children. \"I love you so much.\""},{"time":263385,"text":"Patronizing, I treat everybody from another culture"},{"time":267892,"text":"as if they were my servants."},{"time":270290,"text":"That's why the white people in Africa are called \"bwana,\" boss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276361,"text":"I was given a slap in the face reading a book,"},{"time":279944,"text":"\"Small is Beautiful,\" written by Schumacher, who said,"},{"time":284911,"text":"above all in economic development, if people"},{"time":287869,"text":"do not wish to be helped, leave them alone."},{"time":292424,"text":"This should be the first principle of aid."},{"time":295251,"text":"The first principle of aid is respect."},{"time":298937,"text":"This morning, the gentleman who opened this conference"},{"time":301465,"text":"lay a stick on the floor, and said,"},{"time":305266,"text":"\"Can we -- can you imagine a city"},{"time":309524,"text":"that is not neocolonial?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":313446,"text":"I decided when I was 27 years old"},{"time":317599,"text":"to only respond to people,"},{"time":321806,"text":"and I invented a system called Enterprise Facilitation,"},{"time":326230,"text":"where you never initiate anything,"},{"time":329605,"text":"you never motivate anybody, but you become a servant"},{"time":333827,"text":"of the local passion, the servant of local people"},{"time":337388,"text":"who have a dream to become a better person."},{"time":341786,"text":"So what you do -- you shut up."},{"time":346195,"text":"You never arrive in a community with any ideas,"},{"time":349907,"text":"and you sit with the local people."},{"time":354346,"text":"We don't work from offices."},{"time":356538,"text":"We meet at the cafe. We meet at the pub."},{"time":360504,"text":"We have zero infrastructure."},{"time":363819,"text":"And what we do, we become friends,"},{"time":367146,"text":"and we find out what that person wants to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371906,"text":"The most important thing is passion."},{"time":373764,"text":"You can give somebody an idea."},{"time":376004,"text":"If that person doesn't want to do it,"},{"time":377626,"text":"what are you going to do?"},{"time":381307,"text":"The passion that the person has for her own growth"},{"time":385853,"text":"is the most important thing."},{"time":387579,"text":"The passion that that man has for his own personal growth"},{"time":392136,"text":"is the most important thing."},{"time":393801,"text":"And then we help them to go and find the knowledge,"},{"time":396888,"text":"because nobody in the world can succeed alone."},{"time":402357,"text":"The person with the idea may not have the knowledge,"},{"time":405076,"text":"but the knowledge is available."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407214,"text":"So years and years ago, I had this idea:"},{"time":411073,"text":"Why don't we, for once, instead of arriving in the community"},{"time":415239,"text":"to tell people what to do, why don't, for once,"},{"time":419942,"text":"listen to them? But not in community meetings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424767,"text":"Let me tell you a secret."},{"time":429681,"text":"There is a problem with community meetings."},{"time":434026,"text":"Entrepreneurs never come,"},{"time":437732,"text":"and they never tell you, in a public meeting,"},{"time":440904,"text":"what they want to do with their own money,"},{"time":444520,"text":"what opportunity they have identified."},{"time":448349,"text":"So planning has this blind spot."},{"time":453273,"text":"The smartest people in your community you don't even know,"},{"time":457564,"text":"because they don't come to your public meetings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465404,"text":"What we do, we work one-on-one,"},{"time":469364,"text":"and to work one-on-one, you have to create"},{"time":471077,"text":"a social infrastructure that doesn't exist."},{"time":473752,"text":"You have to create a new profession."},{"time":476324,"text":"The profession is the family doctor of enterprise,"},{"time":481828,"text":"the family doctor of business, who sits with you"},{"time":485399,"text":"in your house, at your kitchen table, at the cafe,"},{"time":488524,"text":"and helps you find the resources to transform your passion"},{"time":492562,"text":"into a way to make a living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494955,"text":"I started this as a tryout in Esperance, in Western Australia."},{"time":500276,"text":"I was a doing a Ph.D. at the time,"},{"time":502528,"text":"trying to go away from this patronizing bullshit"},{"time":506851,"text":"that we arrive and tell you what to do."},{"time":510663,"text":"And so what I did in Esperance that first year"},{"time":515243,"text":"was to just walk the streets, and in three days"},{"time":519869,"text":"I had my first client, and I helped this first guy"},{"time":522763,"text":"who was smoking fish from a garage, was a Maori guy,"},{"time":527308,"text":"and I helped him to sell to the restaurant in Perth,"},{"time":530613,"text":"to get organized, and then the fishermen came to me to say,"},{"time":533743,"text":"\"You the guy who helped Maori? Can you help us?\""},{"time":536729,"text":"And I helped these five fishermen to work together"},{"time":539893,"text":"and get this beautiful tuna not to the cannery in Albany"},{"time":544029,"text":"for 60 cents a kilo, but we found a way"},{"time":547862,"text":"to take the fish for sushi to Japan for 15 dollars a kilo,"},{"time":553213,"text":"and the farmers came to talk to me, said,"},{"time":554735,"text":"\"Hey, you helped them. Can you help us?\""},{"time":557024,"text":"In a year, I had 27 projects going on,"},{"time":559950,"text":"and the government came to see me to say,"},{"time":562102,"text":"\"How can you do that?"},{"time":564489,"text":"How can you do — ?\" And I said, \"I do something very, very, very difficult."},{"time":567815,"text":"I shut up, and listen to them.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573468,"text":"So — (Applause) —"},{"time":581690,"text":"So the government says, \"Do it again.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":586295,"text":"We've done it in 300 communities around the world."},{"time":589453,"text":"We have helped to start 40,000 businesses."},{"time":592988,"text":"There is a new generation of entrepreneurs"},{"time":594660,"text":"who are dying of solitude."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597189,"text":"Peter Drucker, one of the greatest management consultants in history,"},{"time":603348,"text":"died age 96, a few years ago."},{"time":607900,"text":"Peter Drucker was a professor of philosophy"},{"time":609680,"text":"before becoming involved in business,"},{"time":611644,"text":"and this is what Peter Drucker says:"},{"time":614521,"text":"\"Planning is actually incompatible"},{"time":620185,"text":"with an entrepreneurial society and economy.\""},{"time":624434,"text":"Planning is the kiss of death of entrepreneurship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630677,"text":"So now you're rebuilding Christchurch"},{"time":633372,"text":"without knowing what the smartest people in Christchurch"},{"time":636853,"text":"want to do with their own money and their own energy."},{"time":641511,"text":"You have to learn how to get these people"},{"time":644709,"text":"to come and talk to you."},{"time":647706,"text":"You have to offer them confidentiality, privacy,"},{"time":652534,"text":"you have to be fantastic at helping them,"},{"time":656318,"text":"and then they will come, and they will come in droves."},{"time":660312,"text":"In a community of 10,000 people, we get 200 clients."},{"time":663207,"text":"Can you imagine a community of 400,000 people,"},{"time":665779,"text":"the intelligence and the passion?"},{"time":668021,"text":"Which presentation have you applauded the most this morning?"},{"time":671552,"text":"Local, passionate people. That's who you have applauded."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677512,"text":"So what I'm saying is that"},{"time":682783,"text":"entrepreneurship is where it's at."},{"time":685250,"text":"We are at the end of the first industrial revolution --"},{"time":688396,"text":"nonrenewable fossil fuels, manufacturing --"},{"time":691709,"text":"and all of a sudden, we have systems which are not sustainable."},{"time":696166,"text":"The internal combustion engine is not sustainable."},{"time":698813,"text":"Freon way of maintaining things is not sustainable."},{"time":702134,"text":"What we have to look at is at how we"},{"time":705222,"text":"feed, cure, educate, transport, communicate"},{"time":711240,"text":"for seven billion people in a sustainable way."},{"time":714791,"text":"The technologies do not exist to do that."},{"time":718685,"text":"Who is going to invent the technology"},{"time":722053,"text":"for the green revolution? Universities? Forget about it!"},{"time":728551,"text":"Government? Forget about it!"},{"time":731444,"text":"It will be entrepreneurs, and they're doing it now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736698,"text":"There's a lovely story that I read in a futurist magazine"},{"time":739593,"text":"many, many years ago."},{"time":741266,"text":"There was a group of experts who were invited"},{"time":743486,"text":"to discuss the future of the city of New York in 1860."},{"time":748114,"text":"And in 1860, this group of people came together,"},{"time":750604,"text":"and they all speculated about what would happen"},{"time":753551,"text":"to the city of New York in 100 years,"},{"time":755405,"text":"and the conclusion was unanimous:"},{"time":756881,"text":"The city of New York would not exist in 100 years."},{"time":760822,"text":"Why? Because they looked at the curve and said,"},{"time":763083,"text":"if the population keeps growing at this rate,"},{"time":766049,"text":"to move the population of New York around,"},{"time":770185,"text":"they would have needed six million horses,"},{"time":773050,"text":"and the manure created by six million horses"},{"time":776405,"text":"would be impossible to deal with."},{"time":778784,"text":"They were already drowning in manure. (Laughter)"},{"time":784414,"text":"So 1860, they are seeing this dirty technology"},{"time":789463,"text":"that is going to choke the life out of New York."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794281,"text":"So what happens? In 40 years' time, in the year 1900,"},{"time":799410,"text":"in the United States of America, there were 1,001"},{"time":804013,"text":"car manufacturing companies -- 1,001."},{"time":810393,"text":"The idea of finding a different technology"},{"time":813999,"text":"had absolutely taken over,"},{"time":816361,"text":"and there were tiny, tiny little factories in backwaters."},{"time":821277,"text":"Dearborn, Michigan. Henry Ford."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826909,"text":"However, there is a secret to work with entrepreneurs."},{"time":831280,"text":"First, you have to offer them confidentiality."},{"time":834674,"text":"Otherwise they don't come and talk to you."},{"time":837012,"text":"Then you have to offer them absolute, dedicated,"},{"time":841322,"text":"passionate service to them."},{"time":844774,"text":"And then you have to tell them the truth about entrepreneurship."},{"time":848421,"text":"The smallest company, the biggest company,"},{"time":851192,"text":"has to be capable of doing three things beautifully:"},{"time":854582,"text":"The product that you want to sell has to be fantastic,"},{"time":858833,"text":"you have to have fantastic marketing,"},{"time":862657,"text":"and you have to have tremendous financial management."},{"time":866026,"text":"Guess what?"},{"time":868614,"text":"We have never met a single human being"},{"time":871028,"text":"in the world who can make it, sell it and look after the money."},{"time":876675,"text":"It doesn't exist."},{"time":879506,"text":"This person has never been born."},{"time":882256,"text":"We've done the research, and we have looked"},{"time":884748,"text":"at the 100 iconic companies of the world --"},{"time":888699,"text":"Carnegie, Westinghouse, Edison, Ford,"},{"time":893280,"text":"all the new companies, Google, Yahoo."},{"time":895883,"text":"There's only one thing that all the successful companies"},{"time":898559,"text":"in the world have in common, only one:"},{"time":902047,"text":"None were started by one person."},{"time":906582,"text":"Now we teach entrepreneurship to 16-year-olds"},{"time":911084,"text":"in Northumberland, and we start the class"},{"time":914625,"text":"by giving them the first two pages of Richard Branson's autobiography,"},{"time":919049,"text":"and the task of the 16-year-olds is to underline,"},{"time":922886,"text":"in the first two pages of Richard Branson's autobiography"},{"time":926514,"text":"how many times Richard uses the word \"I\""},{"time":929669,"text":"and how many times he uses the word \"we.\""},{"time":932378,"text":"Never the word \"I,\" and the word \"we\" 32 times."},{"time":937118,"text":"He wasn't alone when he started."},{"time":940371,"text":"Nobody started a company alone. No one."},{"time":945415,"text":"So we can create the community"},{"time":948521,"text":"where we have facilitators who come from a small business background"},{"time":951947,"text":"sitting in cafes, in bars, and your dedicated buddies"},{"time":959444,"text":"who will do to you, what somebody did for this gentleman"},{"time":963116,"text":"who talks about this epic,"},{"time":966357,"text":"somebody who will say to you, \"What do you need?"},{"time":968612,"text":"What can you do? Can you make it?"},{"time":970551,"text":"Okay, can you sell it? Can you look after the money?\""},{"time":972801,"text":"\"Oh, no, I cannot do this.\"\"Would you like me to find you somebody?\""},{"time":976555,"text":"We activate communities."},{"time":978643,"text":"We have groups of volunteers supporting the Enterprise Facilitator"},{"time":982687,"text":"to help you to find resources and people"},{"time":985810,"text":"and we have discovered that the miracle"},{"time":988799,"text":"of the intelligence of local people is such"},{"time":991303,"text":"that you can change the culture and the economy"},{"time":995010,"text":"of this community just by capturing the passion,"},{"time":999191,"text":"the energy and imagination of your own people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002828,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}